{
  "stem": "10283.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the meantime, Petain had come to power.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the south of France was no, no longer free.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was under Petain.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Petain took all the Jews out of those camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the German Germans--- non-Jewish Germans he took back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Jewish Germans they took all to Drancy and-- for deportation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I even have the list, the-- what the-- Holocaust Museum in Washington sent me the list, the deportation list out of Drancy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father's name is on it right at  the beginning, with his birth date and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he was not in the best condition already-- you know, two years in the French camps already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he, he went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so did my uncle, apparently.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But Werner was young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was 18.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he had been liberated already by ORT, you know, the ORT organization was big in France.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was not quite 18.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he, he qualified as a child yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was in an ORT school in France.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when the deportations started, the, the mayor of this little town came to the school and said, send-- tomorrow morning, the SS will come and get all the children.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Send the bigger boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Give them whatever you can.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And send them out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They have to fend for themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But they have a chance-- better the chance than sitting here and being picked up tomorrow morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he spoke very well, French.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was very gifted for languages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the meantime, he spoke a very good French.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somehow, through months of walking during the night and sleeping in the fields during the day and working a little bit here and there in the hotels and on farms, he made his way to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he, he came into Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was already there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and we had-- well, I had the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so mother-- here again, we didn't have too much money.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So somehow, we got together with another Belgian Jewish woman who had three children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she needed help with the children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they said, if you'll take care of her and help with the children, she will pay all the expenses for you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We, we had-- we left with 10 marks out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we got together with her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we traveled with her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In different departments, first, we got on the train on, on a Sunday morning to go to, to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, you don't go straight to Switzerland, you know, especially in the middle of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we went-- the first hurdle, of course, was the border into France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You had to get through France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] my mother had made some money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She had about $100 or maybe $200.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we were very much afraid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't want to go without anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But she wanted to-- we didn't know what to do with it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was an interesting thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody put it in shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the shoes were the first thing they put-- the Germans looked at.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had a friend who came from Eastern Europe originally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, ah, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he took a rye bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he cut it in slices.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he put the, the dollar bills in between.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And very fine with the thread, he sewed two slices together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you could not see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And who would look in a bread, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we, we got this-- my mother kept this $100 all through the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we made it over the border somehow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came to the first city where we-- French city where we had to change.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to stay overnight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we got out of the station, out of the train, to get out of the station, there was SS looking at everybody then because they knew that people took this route to go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But mother looked them right straight in the eye.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we walked straight by them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we got out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we stayed overnight in a little hotel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we met up with this lady again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The next morning we had breakfast at a little cafe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were all sitting at the round table, you know, the three children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were, again, four, six people by then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And here comes the SS in again with big chains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had these-- the police had these big, white chains on their helmets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the children were really too little to understand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they were quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we didn't say a word.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I think everybody's heart just stood still, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
